## Verification Plan

### Development Verification
- Run `npm run dev` to start local development server
- Navigate through all pages ensuring proper routing
- Test responsive design at mobile (375px), tablet (768px), desktop (1200px+)
- Verify all animations work smoothly

### Browser Testing
- Open website in browser
- Test navigation between pages
- Test project card hover effects
- Test contact form UI
- Verify external links work

### Manual Verification
- Review visual design matches UI/UX document specifications
- Ensure dark theme, typography, and color palette are correct
- Verify project screenshots load correctly
